    <h2 id="HTML Basic Examples">HTML Basic Examples</h2>
      <h3>View HTML Source Code:</h3>
      <p> <strong>Click + U </strong> in an HTML page, or right-click on the page and select "View Page Source". This will open a new tab containing the HTML source code of the page.</p>
    </section>
    
